### SCIM Configuration

{%- if scim_prefix | upper != 'NONE' %}
| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **SCIM Enabled** | Yes |
| **SCIM Prefix** | {{ scim_prefix | upper }} |
| **Role Owner** | {{ scim_prefix | upper }}_PROVISIONER |
| **User Assignment** | Via identity provider groups |

> **Note:** Roles created for this data product will be owned by `{{ scim_prefix | upper }}_PROVISIONER`. Custom read roles should be assigned to users via your identity provider ({{ scim_prefix }}) group mappings.
{%- else %}
| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **SCIM Enabled** | No |
| **Role Owner** | USERADMIN |
| **User Assignment** | Manual GRANT statements |

> **Note:** Roles created for this data product will be owned by `USERADMIN`. Custom read roles must be manually granted to users.
{%- endif %}

